<div id="homepage" class="row">
	<div class="col-sm-4">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<%= link_to image_tag('blueprint.png', class:'img-circle', style:'background:black'), schemas_path %>
			<div class="caption">
				<h3 class="text-center">Define Event Type</h3>
				<p>Esper require event types to be defined before is can process events. Event types act as blueprint of incomming events.</p>
				<p><%= link_to "Open", schemas_path, class:'btn btn-default btn-block' %></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="col-sm-4">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<%= link_to image_tag('xsd.png', class:'img-circle', style:'background:black'), statements_path %>
			<div class="caption">
				<h3 class="text-center">Create Statement</h3>
				<p>Statements can be defined to filter, process or transform incomming events. After this step you can access statement results page.</p>
				<p><%= link_to "Open", statements_path, class:'btn btn-default btn-block' %></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="col-sm-4">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<%= link_to image_tag('upload.png', class:'img-circle'), stream_index_path %>
			<div class="caption">
				<h3 class="text-center">Upload Events</h3>
				<p>There are multiple ways of delivering events to Esper engine for processing. Two of them (text and file upload) can be accessed here. </p>
				<p><%= link_to "Open", stream_index_path, class:'btn btn-default btn-block' %></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
